d idea.",sft="Mood tracking platform",lft="Business site",uft="Task management platform",cft="Travel blog",dft="Budget tracking platform",fft="Portfolio site",hft="Get inspired on what you can build next",pft="Describe your website or web app",mft="Simply type your idea – or upload an image to get the design or functionality you want.",gft="Make edits easily",vft="Ask AI to update content, design, or layout. Or, edit text yourself with text editing mode.",bft="Go live in 1 click",yft="Publish your website under a custom domain straight from Horizons – in a single click.",wft="Describe your idea or pick a template",Eft="Just tell the AI your idea and see it come to life — or pick a template to get started faster.",Cft="Ask the AI to edit anything — from text and design to functionality. Fine-tune texts and images yourself in the content editor.",Aft="Go live with 1 click",_ft="Launch your website with one click under a custom domain — whenever you’re ready.",Dft="Deleting",kft="Deleted",Sft="Create up to {count} websites",xft="Get a plan to create more websites",Tft="Get a plan to publish your website",Ift="Get a plan to export code",Oft="Export code without limits",Rft="Publish in one click",Mft="Connect a domain",Lft="Get more AI credits",Fft="AI credits",Pft="And much more!",Nft="Get a plan to collaborate with others",Bft="Allow others to edit websites on your selected hosting",jft="Manage roles and permissions securely",zft="Working on it...",$ft="Almost done…",Uft="Last touches...",Hft="Fixing errors...",Vft="Loading...",Wft="For the best results, keep your messages simple, short, and focused on 1 change at a time.",qft="Be specific about what you want to add or change. Avoid messages like “I don’t like this” or “make it different.”",Gft="Add images as a reference for your design or feature idea.",Yft="Check the {link} for step-by-step guides.",Zft="If you run into errors that can’t be fixed after multiple tries, find the last working website version in the chat and click Restore.",Kft="Edit text directly in Preview without using messages. Use the switch in the top-left corner of Preview to turn on editing.",Xft='Select "Edit content" above to change text and images without using messages.',Jft='Click the "Edit" icon above to change text and images without using AI credits.',Qft='Select "Edit text" above to edit content without using messages.',eht="knowledge base",tht="Your Supabase project is paused. If you want to use it, open Supabase to restore it. Once that’s done, refresh the list and connect your project.",nht="Some of your Supabase projects are paused. If you want to use one of them, open Supabase to restore it. Once that’s done, refresh the list and connect your project.",rht="Your connected Supabase project is paused. Open Supabase to restore it if you want to continue using it. Once restored, it will be automatically reconnected to your Horizons project.",oht="Tips",iht="Failed to get referrer URL",aht="Check earnings",sht="Invite a friend and get {count} free AI credits.",lht="Cannot connect project",uht="Please disconnect current project before connecting another one",cht="Disconnect",dht='I have connected my Supabase project "{project}".',fht='I have disconnected my Supabase project "{project}". Please remove all Supabase references in my website.',hht="Connected",pht="Failed to connect Supabase project",mht="Failed to disconnect Supabase project",ght="Failed to duplicate project",vht="Supabase Dashboard",bht="Users management",yht="Table editor",wht="Edge functions",Eht="View Tables",Cht="Supabase Project",Aht="Connect your Supabase project",_ht="This will link your Supabase project to Hostinger Horizons so you can start using backend features like user sign-ups, logins, data storage, and more.",Dht="Disconnect your Supabase project?",kht="This will stop data from syncing between your Hostinger Horizons website and Supabase. You can reconnect it at any time.",Sht="Failed to get Supabase organizations",xht="Failed to authorize Supabase",Tht="Connect",Iht="Add organization",Oht="Add another organization",Rht="Add a new Supabase organization each time you build a website for someone else. For personal projects, you can keep using a single organization.",Mht="This organisation doesn’t have any project. Create project first and then you’ll be able to connect it.",Lht="Beta",Fht="Authorization Successful",Pht="This window will close automatically...",Nht="Supabase",Bht="Stripe",jht="Copy",zht="Copy invite link",$ht="Copied",Uht="Failed to submit feedback",Hht="Failed to delete feedback",Vht="Failed to deploy website",Wht="Failed to create a new website",qht="Failed to get website information",Ght="Failed to get user information",Yht="Failed to get sandbox URL",Zht="Failed to revert to message",Kht="Failed to send message",Xht="Failed to process response",Jht="Failed to Resume Stream",Qht="Application failed to respond in 3 attempts. Please try again later.",ept="Please contact support.",tpt="Failed to get domain",npt="AI credits Limit Reached",rpt="You have reached the maximum number of AI credits allowed",opt="No preview available",ipt="How would you rate Horizons?",apt="We'd love to hear your feedback",spt="Write your feedback here",lpt="Poor",upt="Excellent",cpt="Send",dpt="Stop generation",fpt="Select element in preview",hpt="Element selected — describe the changes",ppt="Select and edit",mpt="Element edit",gpt="Publish",vpt="Publishing",bpt="Publishing changes...",ypt="Publish site",wpt="What do you want to create?",Ept="By continuing, you agree to our {0}",Cpt="Special Terms",Apt="Help guides",_pt="Upload file",Dpt="Upload images",kpt="Enable microphone",Spt="Disable microphone",xpt="Remove file",Tpt="Unsupported file type",Ipt="Some files aren’t supported or exceed the size limit",Opt="Supported formats: JPEG, JPG, PNG, GIF, WEBP. Max size per file: {maxSize}.",Rpt="This file is not supported",Mpt="Supported formats: JPEG, JPG, PNG, GIF, WEBP. Max size per file: {maxSize}.",Lpt="Image file too big",Fpt="The maximum image size is {maxSize}.",Ppt="Image dimensions too large",Npt="Max image dimension: {maxDimension}.",Bpt="Only the following file types are accepted:",jpt="Enhance prompt",zpt="Message limit will renew on {date}",$pt="Upgrade plan",Upt="Upgrade",Hpt="AI credits limit reached",Vpt="Feedback submitted successfully",Wpt="Failed to refresh preview. Please try again later.",qpt="Failed to restart sandbox",Gpt="Please try again later",Ypt="Try again",Zpt="Please refresh the page or try again later",Kpt="Congrats, your site’s now live!",Xpt="Your site’s been updated!",Jpt="Web app is building",Qpt="Landing page",emt=`Create a professional and well-designed (with lighter and vibrant colors) landing page for a book with the following requirements: 
 
Navigation: 
Fixed top navigation menu 
Links to different sections: About, Preview, Author, Reviews 
Prominent 'Buy Now' button 
Smooth scrolling to sections 
 
 
Sections needed: 
Hero section with book introduction and cover image 
Book preview/chapters section 
Author biography with photo 
Customer reviews/testimonials 
Purchase section with pricing 
Newsletter signup 
Footer with contact info 
 
 
Design requirements: 
Modern, clean aesthetic with warm colors (amber/golden tones) 
Responsive design for all devices 
Smooth animations for better engagement 
Professional typography 
Clear call-to-action buttons 
 
Make it visually appealing and optimized for converting visitors into buyers. Add sample information to see the website in action.`,tmt="Budget web app",nmt=`Create a modern and well-designed (with lighter and vibrant colors) budget tracking app with these features: 
Monthly budget management with spent and remaining calculations 
Ability to add and delete expenses with categories 
Visual expense tracking with weekly, monthly, and yearly graphs 
Random budgeting tips display 
Example budget templates 
Modern glassmorphic design with gradient backgrounds 
Smooth animations and transitions 
 
Include sample data (at least 10 expenses) to see the website in action.`,rmt="Resume builder",omt=`Create a modern and well-designed (with lighter and vibrant colors) resume builder web application with the following features: 
 
Sophisticated design 
 
Resume editing features: 
Personal information section with profile picture upload 
Experience management with add/remove functionality 
Multiple template styles (Modern, Classic, Creative) 
Custom color scheme picker 
Live preview mode 
PDF export capability 
 
Technical requirements: 
PDF generation capability 
Responsive design`,imt="Sales pipeline tracker",amt=`Create a beautiful and well-designed (with lighter and vibrant colors) sales pipeline tracker with the following requirements: 
 
Pipeline stages: Lead, Qualified, Proposal, Negotiation, and Closed 
Each deal should include: 
Deal name 
Company name 
Contact person 
Deal value 
Expected close date 
Priority level (High, Medium, Low) 
 
Features needed: 
Drag and drop deals between stages 
Add new deals through a modal form 
Show deal count for each stage 
Priority badges with different colors 
Automatic data saving 
 
