2t="Turn off text editing mode",L2t="Integrations",F2t="Add user sign-ups, logins, data storage, and other backend features.",P2t="Manage products, orders, payments, and more with a built-in admin panel – no prompting needed.",N2t="Track how many visitors you get and the top countries they come from.",B2t="Connect online store",j2t="I've disconnected Online Store integration. Please remove all references/imports from my entire codebase where EcommerceApi.js file is used.",z2t="Orders",$2t="Products",U2t="Discounts",H2t="Categories",V2t="Analytics",W2t="Failed to load analytics",q2t="Settings",G2t="Disconnect store",Y2t="Disconnect online store?",Z2t="This means that all the products you’ve added will be deleted from your website, and checkout will stop working. You can reconnect your store anytime.",K2t="Failed to load store",X2t="Failed to load website data",J2t="Failed to disconnect store",Q2t="Failed to create store",e5t="Online store",t5t="Failed to create online store",n5t="Store manager",r5t="Customers",o5t="Change image",i5t="Upload new image",a5t="Edit content",s5t="What is Supabase?",l5t="How do I connect Supabase to my website?",u5t="Is Supabase free to use?",c5t="Supabase documentation",d5t="Supabase adds backend features to your website – like storing data, handling sign-ups and logins, or syncing updates in real time – without you having to build it all from scratch.",f5t="Think of it as the behind-the-scenes system that powers your website. While Horizons handles what people see (the frontend),  Supabase manages everything in the background (the backend).",h5t="You get all the essentials to make your website run smoothly — so you can focus on building and bringing your ideas to life.",p5t="To connect Supabase to your website: {0}",m5t="Click ‘Connect’ above. You’ll be redirected to Supabase, where you can log in to an existing Supabase account or create a new one.",g5t="Select the organization you want to manage through Horizons. If you don’t have an organization, create one.",v5t="Once you’re redirected back to Horizons, connect a Supabase project by clicking ‘Connect’. You can also create a new project by clicking ‘Create new project‘.",b5t="Confirm the connection and wait until everything’s set up. You can track the progress in the chat.",y5t="Supabase has a free tier, and paid plans are available if you need more resources like storage, bandwidth, or other advanced features.",w5t="See more information on their {0}.",E5t="pricing page",C5t="If you have any questions about Supabase, {0}.",A5t="see documentation",_5t="What can I sell?",D5t="What payment methods are supported?",k5t="What shipping methods are supported?",S5t="How do I connect an online store to my website?",x5t="How do I edit my online store?",T5t="You can sell physical and digital products, gift cards, and accept donations.",I5t="Subscriptions and appointments aren’t supported yet, but you can still offer them using third-party tools:",O5t="To start selling subscriptions, we recommend using Stripe. Just ask Horizons to help you connect it to your website.",R5t="For appointments, tools like Calendly work great. You can also ask Horizons how to add it to your site.",M5t="Choose from {0}, like cards, PayPal, Google Pay, Apple Pay, and others. Payment methods available for your store depend on where you’re selling, your location, currency, and who you’re selling to.",L5t="100+ payment methods",F5t="Once you connect an online store, you can define your shipping zones with up to 25 delivery options and set custom shipping rules based on order amount or item weight.",P5t="Click ‘Connect’ above and wait till Horizons sets it up for you.",N5t="Once the store’s connected, click ‘Integrations’ → ‘Online store’ to access all the online store settings.",B5t="You can manage your store anytime by clicking ‘Integrations’ → ‘Online store’.",j5t="Once it’s connected, you’ll see links that will redirect you to the built-in store manager. From there, you can manage products, payments, and more – without any prompting needed.",z5t="If you want to edit the way your online store looks (like the layout of your product list), just ask AI in the chat to make changes.",$5t="Connecting",U5t="Quick answers",H5t="Preview",V5t="Edit text",W5t="Code",q5t="Data",G5t="Discard",Y5t="Save",Z5t="Code changes saved.",K5t="You have unsaved changes.",X5t="Code changes couldn't be saved. Try saving again.",J5t="Saving changes...",Q5t="Select file to edit",evt="Save or discard code changes to exit the code editor.",tvt="Save or discard code changes to send the message.",nvt="Disable 'Select and edit' to change modes.",rvt="Feature roadmap",ovt="Ask Kodee",ivt=`Hi, I’m Kodee, your AI assistant.
