, and others by simply chatting with AI",M4t="Free in beta – we’ll let you know before any pricing changes.",L4t="Got it",F4t="Use ‘Test data’ to:",P4t="Safely test new changes and view data from preview mode. E.g. if you test a contact form in your site’s preview, you'll see submitted data here.",N4t="Use ‘Live data’ to:",B4t="See real data collected from your published site, like new signups or form submissions from visitors.",j4t="Learn more",z4t="Get more AI credits to build without limits",$4t="Supabase project is not ready yet",U4t="Domain connected, but it may take some time to go live",H4t="If you can't reach your website using your domain, that means your domain is still connecting. This can take up to 24 hours.",V4t="Supabase project not found - proceeding without it",W4t="We couldn't find the Supabase project you're trying to connect. Website will be created without it.",q4t="Earn money with Horizons",G4t="Invite others to try Horizons and earn up to {referralEarningsAmount} for each person who buys their first plan.",Y4t="Thinking",Z4t="Working",K4t="Stopping",X4t="Reverting",J4t="Loading changes",Q4t="Loading preview",ebt="Selecting images",tbt="Selected images",nbt="Checking details",rbt="Checked details",obt="Enabling data storage",ibt="Enabled data storage",abt="Editing data storage",sbt="Edited data storage",lbt="Your site is live",ubt="Domain",cbt="Last publish",dbt="Connect domain",fbt="Publish changes",hbt="Your site’s domain",pbt="Introducing built-in backend",mbt="Creating advanced websites with features like user accounts and booking forms is easier than ever. Just describe the features you need in chat and Horizons will handle all the rest. No external tools needed.",gbt="Data dashboard",vbt="Your data dashboard will appear here once you ask Horizons to add features that require data collection (e.g., user accounts or contact forms).",bbt="Message examples",ybt="Add user accounts to my project.",wbt="Add a page with contact form that has name